check_in_instructions:
Thank you so much for booking! Your door code and additional access instructions will be texted to you on the day of arrival. If you do not receive them two hours prior to check-in, please reach out to us via call or text at 615-334-0695.
 
*Important Update*  
Weâ€™re thrilled to welcome so many guests this season! To ensure every stay is absolutely perfect, we won't be able to accommodate early check-in or late check-out requests until after Labor Day. This gives our dedicated team the necessary time to clean and inspect each property thoroughly, making sure everything is just right for your arrival.
 
But hereâ€™s some good news! If your property is ready earlier, youâ€™ll receive a notification along with your door code on the day of your arrival. So, thereâ€™s always a chance for a pleasant surprise!
 
We appreciate your understanding and patience as we focus on providing top-notch service and handling any urgent needs that might come up during your stay. Your comfort and satisfaction are our top priorities!
 
Thank you for being amazing guests, and we canâ€™t wait for you to enjoy your stay with us!

CHECK IN INSTRUCTIONS:
Access and Parking:
Parking is available for up to 6 vehicles in the circle Driveway.
 
Access Instructions:
Once parked, follow to the main door which is on the side of the house facing the parking area and it is equipped with a keyless entry lock.
 
Lock Instructions:
- Use the code provided above for entry access.  The check mark button is located on the bottom left of the keypad and must be pushed after entering code.
If you are unable to unlock the door, please call 615-334-0695 and a Grand Welcome representative will assist you.

To lock the door when leaving the home:
- The door does NOT lock automatically so please press any key on the keypad to lock when you leave.
- If you are unable to lock the door, please call at 615-334-0695 and a Grand Welcome representative will assist you.
 
Wireless Internet Information:
Network: ZenLodge 
Password: 351elmlodge!
 
Washer and Dryer:
Washer and dryer are located in the laundry room on the 2nd floor near the living room.
 
Trash:
Trash is picked up on Wednesday. The bins are located near the black iron gate at driveway.  If trash day falls during your stay, please take bins to the street - please do not block the mailboxes.  
 
Additional Information:
- Take a quick inventory of the kitchen and bath items that are provided before you go to the store to ensure you will have everything you need for your stay. We provide a starter set of amenities, but for longer stays you will likely want to get more. These complimentary amenities are provided free of charge and are included in the blue boxes in the kitchen and bathrooms so please help yourselves! Nearest grocery store is 2.5 miles away at 215 Ranch Road 2900, Kingsland.
- This home is not pet friendly. If there is evidence found of an animal presence during your stay or post check-out, you will be charged additional cleaning fees.
- No Smoking Allowed Anywhere Inside or Outside.  If evidence is found, you will be charged additional fees. 
- There are paddleboards, kayaks, lily pad, paddles, and life vests available for guest use.  Please put back all equipment back in the same place that you found them after use.
-If bringing a boat or jet skis, there are several options for tying off your boat and/or jet skis. Boat and jet skis at property are owners and not for guest use. Boats can be launched at Kingsland Community Park located at 155 Lions Park Road, Kingsland, TX 78639.  There is a $10 launch fee - there is no overnight trailer parking at boat launch. Guests may park boat trailers at property.   
 
Check-Out:
- Please leave the house as you found it - nice and tidy.  Please return any items used to it's original location.
- Set AC to 78 degrees during the summer months when checking out. - Set heater to 58 degrees during winter months when checking out.
- Bag all garbage and place in trash cans outside.
- Load all dirty dishes into the dishwasher and start.
- If the grill was used, please clean after use. If not left cleaned, a $25 fee will be charged.
- Please lock the door before your departure. We hope you enjoy your stay and invite you to share your experience.

If you feel you will be unable to provide a 5-Star review, please contact our Customer Care Team at 615-334-0695 to discuss your concerns
